phrases: Father!

Yes.

Yes.

Yes.

That is...

I happened to see Aunt

Exceptionally beautiful!

Yes.

- Yes. -
That is so.

Sit properly.

Hurry!
Help!
Help!

Your Highness.

Father.

Sister.

Tell him that I, your brother

Fresh peach blossom facial cream.
